Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the groups that the Sweats Club helped out for this year's Oraga Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all of them fall under our club's exhibit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you come to that conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in trying to reason with Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the Sweats Club will proceed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to check out all the exhibits!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, do we have to wear these sweats?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Sweats Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the sweats are the master, the skirt is a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a joke, just right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we tell Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will confront the next enemy attack{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with just the two of you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Make sure Kyono doesn't know about this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Mr. Tadokoro is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old man can be quite thoughtful at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you whispering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Lan, you're so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about that meanie Lan, let's just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muginami, don't pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The live concert starts in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's check out the haunted house first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But I'm also kind of hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if people will come to our café...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look perfect for the role, Michi. Be more confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so lucky, Sachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Surfing Club attracts a lot of attention because you won the prefectural competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'll let Le Garite have the Vox.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I've already given up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just doesn't sit right with me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to fight the Chairman and the people of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl has got you on her leash, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is that the extent of your feelings towards Yurikano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that supposed to be a bad joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what did Yurikano hope for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we first came to this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was determined to accomplish our goal no matter what it took.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But would Yurikano really want us to fight to avenge her death?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is revenge worth the sacrifice of so many lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't Yurikano's greatest wish
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be to stop the Vox from causing any more suffering?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.10,0:06:17.77,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\bord0\fs15\fnBloody\pos(695,245)\c&H414CD5&}The Ghost\N Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:17.77,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1&H80&\bord1.5\fs15\fnBloody\pos(695,245)\c&HFAFBFF&\3c&HFBFDF2&}The Ghost\N Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two helped this club with their makeup, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks, it's so silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're afraid of ghosts, right, Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not! I did the makeup, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this, I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Care to try some corn on the cob?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving! I want to go home, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan, your eyes are all red!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this and cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially that last scene, where...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that you, Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing! It's a huge hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, when the lead actress is attractive,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the film just blossoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, who are these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, they're members of our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:08:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! You both must be in our next film!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Be in"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just looking at you gets my creative juices flowing!{Mmmm, loli's flowing juices..}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, where to next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to take a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll print it right out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you crouch down a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All her shots are double taps!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise the level of difficulty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't even count as practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Japanese carnival is not as spectacular as I had imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a high school arts festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asteria, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our club is in trouble! Please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a way for the Sweats Club to enjoy the Oraga Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Madoka. We owe you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I didn't know Lan and Sachi were such good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are. You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muginami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Michi, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but would you mind helping us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're shorthanded at the Astronomy Club's café.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They need you, Muginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Muginami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these are grilled eels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eels... Did you say eels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're swimming around in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually eat those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so black and thin and long... slimy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can eel taste so good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I never informed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should decide either to be upset or to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyono Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me all the cuisine that is being served at this carnival!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, why is it that the unhealthier the food looks, the better it tastes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being overdramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The human body is made up of what you eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And our hearts and minds cannot work if we don't have a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To eat is to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are connected to the universe by the food we eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the water we drink, and the air we breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put something into our mouths means to take the universe into our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... What? Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our planetarium show is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The room will darken, so please hang on to your belongings and watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a huge help, Muginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, coming right away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, please wait just a moment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know quite a bit about stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you join the Astronomy Club, Muginami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to do the Planetarium Café again next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please join!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we used the ultimate weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we were forsaken by heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not have noticed, but you're quite popular, Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:25.82,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(0,0)\bord0\blur1\p1\c&HE3E6EA&}m 588 248 l 603 410 l 810 364 l 794 194 {p0}
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.80,0:13:25.82,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fscx95\fscy115\fax-0.15\fs45\an8\bord0\c&HF6CB60&\fnJennifer's Hand Writing\b1\frx10\fry350\frz13.84\pos(682,260)}Welcome to\N{\fs43} the Surf Club
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so sure that if you wore a wetsuit, we'd have a flood of customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was too optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't attract customers when I can't even swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You were worried about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll teach you how to swim next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In appreciation for helping me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyono Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be happy seeing Lan and Muginami
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making new friends and having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But instead, I'm feeling a bit depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was all by myself at last year's arts festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm not sure why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Tadokoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A large number of artificial objects have been spotted
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,approaching Earth at a high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharos is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's moving into battle position
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to keep this town out of harm's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Midori, I can...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Lan and Muginami are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are already on their way to Pharos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tadokoro ordered them to keep the assault a secret from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He acted under my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a lie!{\i0}
