Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you've run the Sweats Club all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now you have Lan and Muginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you got upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You learned that they had spent some time on their own
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and could experience joy without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're remembering the fear of losing someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Madoka is mad at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the only way to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can't have Aura act up like the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made our choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect Madoka along with this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean, protect Kamogawa together with Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or protect both Madoka and this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Yoko filled me in on the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Big Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to sea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's boat is in the harbor. Use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To fight means coming face-to-face
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the fear of losing something precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared to confront that fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan! Muginami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They actually got a clubroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those damn kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our time, we had to do our activities without a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about letting Madoka go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have stopped her even if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just like her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're more fixated on that than Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Machiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Commencing transport to the catapult deck.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lympha now entering T.O. sequence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ignis now entering T.O. sequence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:18:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Commencing Vox Ignis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really going to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}A.I Remote System check.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have to fight Brother this time, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Probably.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hesitate again, Lan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you do, I'll smack you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan, you sound like Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Opening the top hatch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Sweats Club.{timing might work better joined with the line two above this?]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Vox Lympha is on deck.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Vox Ignis is on deck.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vox Lympha, Vox Ignis, cleared for take-off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Orca!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it our all, Hupo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the status of the Le Garite armada?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We lured them into the Starburst Region in the Thaddeus Nebula.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It will be difficult for them to escape from there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are our losses?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The High Speed Cruiser {\i0}Forzellhind{\i1} was destroyed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Artillery Ship, {\i0}Dahhau II{\i1}, sustained serious damage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And we lost ten Ovids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's less than our initial estimates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But higher than my hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I miscalculated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're too rigid with your estimates, Grania.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay on course to enter orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Operations will begin shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you sure about this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for what I'm about to make you go through...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're following Yurikano.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed that you kept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we do it, for old times' sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. It's the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But getting it ready now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A schoolteacher has quite a bit of influence, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do, Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I turn back to shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,decided to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:23:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
